__Comment:
Width/Height are the maximum sizes these images can scale to in blocks.
PermLevel is the default Minecraft permission system to use slapmap commands. It defaults to 4 which is only operators with a level of 4 can use it. Set it to 0 to let anyone use it.
MultiplayerWorldName is the name of the world in which your data folder where all the maps are stored is. It defaults to world but you might need to change this if you changed your world's name.
